# Claude Software Factory TUI (modular)

Modular Textual TUI for orchestrating the Claude Software Factory workflow.

Install (editable):

```bash
pip install -e .
```

Run TUI:

```bash
csf-tui --command "python3 tools/claude_orchestrator_runner.py" --cwd /path/to/project
```

Run headless:

```bash
csf-tui --mode headless --view summary --simulate
```

Tests

```bash
pytest -q
```

Notes
- Set `CSF_TUI_VIEWER_PATH` to point to a `state-machine-viewer.py` if not colocated.
- The TUI supports scheduling a one-time future start via Command Palette: "Schedule Start".
